---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us | ToolzTotal"
  description="About ToolzTotal. Discover why we built a clean, ad-free, and privacy-first calculator platform for developers, finance and daily utilities."
>
  <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
    <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
    <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-8 text-xs font-mono text-mute">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors font-sans">Home</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span class="text-ink">About Us</span>
    </nav>

    <article class="prose max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink font-sans mb-8">
        About ToolzTotal
      </h1>
      
      <div class="space-y-8 text-body text-base font-sans leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-lg text-ink font-semibold">
          ToolzTotal was born out of frustration with modern utility sites.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          If you have ever tried to calculate a mortgage payment, generate a QR code, or estimate a personal loan, you know what the current internet looks like. You are greeted by slow loading speeds, paragraphs of keyword-stuffed SEO text designed to trick search engines, blinking display ads, autoplay video players, and forms demanding your email address just to show you a simple number.
        </p>

        <p>
          We decided to build a clean, fast, and privacy-first alternative.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mt-8">Our Core Principles</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="border border-hairline p-5 rounded-lg bg-canvas shadow-lvl2">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-ink mb-2">1. 100% Client-Side</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">
              Every formula and logic runs locally in your browser. None of your calculations are ever uploaded, recorded, or sent to a database.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-hairline p-5 rounded-lg bg-canvas shadow-lvl2">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-ink mb-2">2. Zero Signup Required</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">
              You do not need to create an account, log in, or input your email to access any tool. Just open the page, get your answer, and carry on.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-hairline p-5 rounded-lg bg-canvas shadow-lvl2">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-ink mb-2">3. Blazing Fast</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">
              Built using Astro's static site architecture, our pages load instantly and adapt perfectly to any mobile, tablet, or desktop screen.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-hairline p-5 rounded-lg bg-canvas shadow-lvl2">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-ink mb-2">4. Completely Clutter-Free</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">
              No popups, no tracking cookies, and no layout shifts. Just a stark, clean layout inspired by developer dashboard designs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mt-8">Who is ToolzTotal for?</h2>
        <p>
          Whether you are a developer formatting text, a home buyer calculating mortgage options, or a freelancer estimating self-employment tax liabilities, ToolzTotal provides the mathematical clarity you need without the digital clutter. 
        </p>

        <p class="pt-6">
          <a href="/#search-section" class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center bg-primary text-on-primary hover:bg-mute font-sans text-sm font-medium px-6 rounded-full transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-lvl2">
            Browse our calculators
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>
